---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Automações | Engenharia e Code" description="Scripts e ferramentas de automação.">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
		<header class="mb-12">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Automações & Scripts</h1>
			<p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">
				Coleção de scripts Python e Node.js que desenvolvi para otimizar fluxos de trabalho. 
				Foco em produtividade e eliminação de tarefas repetitivas.
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
			<!-- Automation Card 1 -->
			<article class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-colors">
				<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
					<div class="badge bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono">Python</div>
					<a href="#" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"/></svg>
					</a>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">SEO Keyword Analyzer</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-4">
					Script que analisa densidade de palavras-chave em listas de URLs e gera relatórios automáticos.
				</p>
				<div class="bg-slate-950 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-800 font-mono text-xs text-emerald-400 overflow-x-auto">
					$ python analyze.py --url example.com
				</div>
			</article>

			<!-- Automation Card 2 -->
			<article class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-colors">
				<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
					<div class="badge bg-yellow-500/10 text-yellow-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono">Node.js</div>
					<a href="#" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"/></svg>
					</a>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Image Optimizer Pipeline</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-4">
					Pipeline CI/CD para converter e otimizar assets automaticamente para WebP/Avif.
				</p>
				<div class="bg-slate-950 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-800 font-mono text-xs text-emerald-400 overflow-x-auto">
					$ npm run optimize:assets
				</div>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
